{"parse":{"title":"Raw Loch Frenzy","pageid":38406,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|c=2}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_03\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=6317\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=15\n|name=Raw Loch Frenzy\n|level=5\n|effect=Use: Restores 61 health over 18 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nThis item drops from [[Loch Frenzy]] in [[Loch Modan]]. <br/>\nThis item can also be [[fishing|fished]] from [[Loch Modan]].\n\n==Raw Loch Frenzy as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{item|icon=|Loch Frenzy Delight}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6317}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_loch_frenzy.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]"}}}